com.tomtom.speedtools.objects

Class Immutables

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tomtom.speedtools.objects.Immutables

  • public final class Immutables
extends Object
    Utility methods to work with immutable data structures. These methods rely on Google immutable libraries and provide a convenience layer on top of them.
